Arabesque Partners (or Arabesque Asset Management) is an Anglo-German investment management firm founded in 2013, with headquarters in London and a research hub in Frankfurt. The company offers a quantitative approach to sustainable investing.
Arabesque combines systematic portfolio technology with the values of the United Nations Global Compact, the United Nations Principles for Responsible Investment (UN PRI) and balance sheet and business activity screening.
Central to Arabesqueâ€™s investment process is the integration of non-financial Environmental, Social and Governance (ESG) information into fundamental and quantitative financial models.
